---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Changelog">
  <div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-display-lg text-ink font-bold mb-2">Changelog & Updates</h1>
      <p class="text-body-md text-muted">Keep track of the latest updates, features, and improvements made to ToolBundle.</p>
    </div>

    {/* Timeline Card */}
    <div class="card shadow-sm p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        {/* v0.3.0 */}
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start relative">
          <div class="absolute left-2.5 top-6 bottom-[-40px] w-0.5 bg-hairline" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-primary/20 text-on-primary font-bold text-[10px]" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);">
            ⚡
          </span>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 pl-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
              <h2 class="text-heading-md font-bold text-ink m-0">v0.3.0</h2>
              <span class="badge text-[10px] py-0.5 px-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary border border-primary/20 rounded font-semibold">Latest</span>
              <time class="text-caption text-xs text-muted font-medium">May 30, 2026</time>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body-sm text-muted space-y-2 pl-1 mt-2">
              <li>Migrated settings and changelog modals into <strong>dedicated standalone pages</strong> (`/settings` and `/changelog`) to improve usability and accommodate future upgrades.</li>
              <li>Replaced all legacy theme components with a highly responsive, custom theme toggle layout.</li>
              <li>Tuned Light/Dark mode options with support for Automatic System syncing.</li>
              <li>Implemented <strong>Accent color customization</strong> (Red, Blue, Green, Purple, Amber) with zero-flash rendering.</li>
              <li>Added Language selector (English / Tiếng Việt) & browser storage manager.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* v0.2.0 */}
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start relative">
          <div class="absolute left-2.5 top-6 bottom-[-40px] w-0.5 bg-hairline" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-canvas border border-hairline flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[10px] text-muted">
            •
          </span>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 pl-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
              <h2 class="text-heading-sm font-bold text-ink m-0">v0.2.0</h2>
              <time class="text-caption text-xs text-muted font-medium">May 29, 2026</time>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body-sm text-muted space-y-2 pl-1 mt-2">
              <li>Overhauled individual blog pages with a <strong>Sticky Table of Contents sidebar</strong> on desktop.</li>
              <li>Added a collapsible, interactive accordion Index panel for mobile layouts.</li>
              <li>Added a sleek, red sticky <strong>Reading Progress bar</strong> at the top of the viewport.</li>
              <li>Implemented in-depth scroll-spy tracking highlights on active sections.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* v0.1.5 */}
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start relative">
          <div class="absolute left-2.5 top-6 bottom-[-40px] w-0.5 bg-hairline" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-canvas border border-hairline flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[10px] text-muted">
            •
          </span>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 pl-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
              <h2 class="text-heading-sm font-bold text-ink m-0">v0.1.5</h2>
              <time class="text-caption text-xs text-muted font-medium">May 20, 2026</time>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body-sm text-muted space-y-2 pl-1 mt-2">
              <li>Promoted the <strong>Workflow Canvas Builder</strong> to a primary feature in the header menu.</li>
              <li>Optimized client-side canvas block connections and custom scripts configuration.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* v0.1.0 */}
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-canvas border border-hairline flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[10px] text-muted">
            •
          </span>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 pl-2">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
              <h2 class="text-heading-sm font-bold text-ink m-0">v0.1.0</h2>
              <time class="text-caption text-xs text-muted font-medium">May 1, 2026</time>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-body-sm text-muted space-y-2 pl-1 mt-2">
              <li>Initial release of <strong>ToolBundle</strong> with 100+ fully offline-first utility tools.</li>
              <li>Implemented client-side PDF, image, text, math, and color processors.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
